1. *Podrumu* nisam dugo posetio. (I haven't visited the basement in a long time.)
2. Ona je pripremala hranu u *podrumu*. (She was preparing food in the basement.)
3. Pre nego što smo otišli, proverili smo *podrum*. (Before we left, we checked the basement.)
4. On je čuval svoje dragocenosti u *podrumu*. (He was keeping his valuables in the basement.)
5. Ona je bila sama u *podrumu*. (She was alone in the basement.)